285
00:24:16,070 --> 00:24:18,910
Your daughter will be here soon.

286
00:24:18,910 --> 00:24:21,560
I don't know how to thank you enough.

287
00:24:24,100 --> 00:24:25,720
 Yu Yi Hwa

288
00:24:43,600 --> 00:24:46,130
I couldn't do the laundry because I ran out of detergent.

289
00:24:46,130 --> 00:24:48,150
You're so sweet.

290
00:24:51,540 --> 00:24:55,560
