306
00:25:58,160 --> 00:26:00,040
Today?

307
00:26:01,200 --> 00:26:02,800
Should I take it out as a check?

308
00:26:02,800 --> 00:26:05,220
All of it in cash.

309
00:26:06,100 --> 00:26:09,400
