310
00:26:09,970 --> 00:26:14,100
You have to look good to make a lot of money.

311
00:26:15,390 --> 00:26:20,180
Some women say spending money on clothes is pointless since they'll come off fast,

312
00:26:20,180 --> 00:26:22,160
but I disagree.

313
00:26:22,820 --> 00:26:25,800
My place is on a different level.

314
00:26:29,100 --> 00:26:33,200
Please sign to confirm that you received the money.

315
00:26:33,200 --> 00:26:37,600
This is the new two-year term plan you're signing up for—

316
00:26:37,600 --> 00:26:41,130
Doesn't the five-year one have a better interest rate?

317
00:26:42,630 --> 00:26:46,040
It's not that much more. Rather than signing up for a long-term plan

318
00:26:46,040 --> 00:26:48,810
and forgetting about it again— 
 - No.

319
00:26:48,810 --> 00:26:52,940
Even if it gets me 1,000 won more, I prefer that. I want the five-year one.

320
00:26:52,940 --> 00:26:54,560
Sure.

321
00:26:56,000 --> 00:27:01,300
The girls from other places ended up with nothing,

322
00:27:01,300 --> 00:27:06,750
