I know it feels uncomfortable to work for VIPs in the uniform.

328
00:27:51,890 --> 00:27:57,010
Feel free to wear normal clothes. But wear the name tag, still.

329
00:27:57,010 --> 00:27:59,600
- Yes.
 - How about lunch?

330
00:27:59,600 --> 00:28:01,500
Are you having it with a VIP?

