00:32:55,750 --> 00:32:59,350
- Did you prepare this yourself? 
 - Prepare?

372
00:32:59,350 --> 00:33:01,630
It's my dad's recipe.

373
00:33:01,630 --> 00:33:04,290
He just made two soups when I was a kid.

374
00:33:04,290 --> 00:33:06,550
It was miyeokguk* and this.
  (Seaweed soup)

375
00:33:06,550 --> 00:33:09,600
It's like my comfort food.

376
00:33:09,600 --> 00:33:13,300
You said your father is at a nursing home, right?

377
00:33:17,300 --> 00:33:19,170
Thank you.

378
00:33:19,170 --> 00:33:20,330
Pardon?

379
00:33:20,330 --> 00:33:23,360
I love being together like this.

380
00:33:24,400 --> 00:33:28,900
If I were alone, I would've been looking for a job, comparing hourly pay.

381
00:33:28,900 --> 00:33:32,910
Because private loan interests double overnight.

382
00:33:32,910 --> 00:33:35,420
Did you get a private loan?

383
00:33:44,970 --> 00:33:49,930
 So now you're just working on the script instead of working?

384
00:33:51,200 --> 00:33:54,200
 Yes, I want to focus on it.

385
00:34:03,900 --> 00:34:06,000
Hello.

386
00:34:07,600 --> 00:34:09,500
Hello.

387
00:34:10,600 --> 00:34:12,500
Have a seat here.

388
00:34:18,070 --> 00:34:20,130
Excuse me.

389
00:34:25,820 --> 00:34:27,920
It's all right.

390
00:34:38,970 --> 00:34:42,780
 Here's an announcement. On the busy train...

391
00:34:42,780 --> 00:34:44,800
