405
00:35:42,020 --> 00:35:44,980
Sure.

406
00:35:44,980 --> 00:35:46,780
 The doors are open.

407
00:35:46,780 --> 00:35:48,790
Thank you.

408
00:36:15,490 --> 00:36:18,350
Gosh, looks so tasty.

409
00:36:20,280 --> 00:36:23,780
It's better to put the light here. It makes the room look bigger.

410
00:36:25,950 --> 00:36:27,600
It feels like something's missing.

411
00:36:27,600 --> 00:36:29,670
Hold on a second.

412
00:36:32,050 --> 00:36:34,080
Okay.

413
00:36:37,340 --> 00:36:38,930
It's so cute.

414
00:36:38,930 --> 00:36:41,080
You're so girly.

415
00:36:41,720 --> 00:36:44,670
- Let's eat quickly. The food is getting cold. 
 - Eonni,

416
00:36:44,670 --> 00:36:46,720
what's your secret?

417
00:36:47,720 --> 00:36:50,550
I put soda in the boiled soy sauce,

418
00:36:50,550 --> 00:36:52,900
and added garlic, ginger—

419
00:36:52,900 --> 00:36:54,280
Yuzu.

420
00:36:54,280 --> 00:36:55,650
Huh?

421
00:36:56,500 --> 00:37:01,900
Cook licorice and yuzu in the soy sauce and...

422
00:37:07,220 --> 00:37:09,730
- What's this?
- It's a black tea.

423
00:37:09,730 --> 00:37:13,510
It's trendy these days because the CEO of AF Department Store posted it on social media.

424
00:37:13,510 --> 00:37:16,340
Is it expensive? How much does this cost?

425
00:37:16,340 --> 00:37:19,330
You always ask how much things are.

426
00:37:20,880 --> 00:37:25,460
I dodged being humiliated, thanks to you, Ms. Se Ju.

427
00:37:25,460 --> 00:37:29,210
How did you know, by the way? It was on the staff group chat.

428
00:37:29,210 --> 00:37:30,540
I heard it from a nurse.

429
00:37:30,540 --> 00:37:34,000
She apparently saw Shi Eun's patients watching the video.

430
00:37:34,000 --> 00:37:35,980
I guess she works at the company.

431
00:37:35,980 --> 00:37:38,930
She recognized your face and told me.

432
00:37:39,900 --> 00:37:44,700
Thanks to your video, I was commissioned to promote something on social media.

433
00:37:44,700 --> 00:37:47,180
I'll treat you to a meal if it works out.

434
00:37:49,850 --> 00:37:53,190
By the way, does Tae Mi's dad still play tennis these days?

435
00:37:53,190 --> 00:37:55,970
He even skips lunch appointments twice a week.

436
00:37:55,970 --> 00:37:58,500
During the day? Twice a week?

437
00:37:58,500 --> 00:38:00,130
How about in the evening, then?

438
00:38:00,130 --> 00:38:04,910
In the evening, he goes almost every day to stop by the sauna, too.

439
00:38:04,910 --> 00:38:08,320
He's a member of the hotel tennis court.

440
00:38:08,320 --> 00:38:10,710
A hotel member.

441
00:38:10,710 --> 00:38:13,730
He must take a shower there every day, then.

442
00:38:16,040 --> 00:38:17,590
Why do you ask, Eonni?

443
00:38:17,590 --> 00:38:19,920
Are you worried he'd cheat on me?

444
00:38:24,010 --> 00:38:26,070
Aren't you worried?

445
00:38:29,520 --> 00:38:33,980
He's devoted to me, almost every night.

446
00:38:33,980 --> 00:38:37,260
He's in his 40s. How could he do more than that?

447
00:38:39,160 --> 00:38:41,570
Gosh, you're making me blush.

448
00:38:41,570 --> 00:38:44,750
And during the day,

449
00:38:44,750 --> 00:38:46,580
he plays tennis, too?

450
00:38:46,580 --> 00:38:49,850
He gets a lot of male patients at the dermatology clinic, too.

451
00:38:49,850 --> 00:38:54,470
He doesn't go to the hotel tennis court for no reason. It's for his business.

452
00:38:54,470 --> 00:38:57,730
He started going there because I suggested it.

453
00:38:57,730 --> 00:38:59,790
I see...

454
00:39:18,390 --> 00:39:22,740
Assistant Manager, I never got to call you back. I'm sorry.

455
00:39:22,740 --> 00:39:26,440
Ms. Yu Yi Hwa, you almost caused serious trouble.

456
00:39:27,500 --> 00:39:29,800
Do you handle several 100 million won

457
00:39:29,800 --> 00:39:31,900
just like that?

458
00:39:35,600 --> 00:39:37,900
How come every client you meet

459
00:39:37,900 --> 00:39:42,500
deposits 200 or 300 million won with you?

460
00:39:43,590 --> 00:39:47,280
Your client's son came by and said you did things that even he finds tough to do.

461
00:39:47,280 --> 00:39:49,300
He wanted me to give you this.

462
00:39:51,900 --> 00:39:53,560
It's pretty hefty.

463
00:39:53,560 --> 00:39:54,900
Wow...

464
00:39:54,900 --> 00:39:57,130
If you raise 200 million more next month,

465
00:39:57,130 --> 00:40:01,930
