466
00:40:01,930 --> 00:40:04,680
Her track record is on a godly level.

467
00:40:04,680 --> 00:40:07,490
She even changes a client's diaper.

468
00:40:07,490 --> 00:40:11,220
She must've looked for opportunities by going to townhouses.

469
00:40:11,220 --> 00:40:12,410
She did.

470
00:40:12,410 --> 00:40:16,540
How come every old lady she meets deposits 200 or 300 million won regularly?

471
00:40:16,540 --> 00:40:18,280
There's something strange about that woman.

472
00:40:18,280 --> 00:40:20,110
I'll give you a vacation as a reward.

473
00:40:20,110 --> 00:40:23,400
Rest several days more after the coming holiday.

474
00:40:23,400 --> 00:40:25,330
You can take a trip abroad, too.

475
00:40:25,330 --> 00:40:26,640
Thank you.

